  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/14c22cf84985625154d9a85ed34967fe.avif?t=1739988118\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SPELLHACK!! </strong>is a survival deckbuilder that features fast-paced, arcadey combat and a surreal 1980s setting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the <strong>day</strong>, you have 12 hours to spend improving your Spelldrive and collecting new Technospells. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At <strong>night</strong>, the Summoned Beasts descend upon you. You'll need to think fast to survive  12 hours of nighttime before the next day arrives!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/3a69eb9e9e93b2cc6874d2b6ef8f371a.poster.avif?t=1739988118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/3a69eb9e9e93b2cc6874d2b6ef8f371a.webm?t=1739988118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/3a69eb9e9e93b2cc6874d2b6ef8f371a.mp4?t=1739988118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SPELLHACK!! Floppy Disk Contents:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>Story Mode</strong> to ease into the pace and mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>Challenge Mode with 5 levels</strong>  to really test your skills!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>150+ Technospells</strong> to collect and install </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>50+ Summoned Beasts</strong> to repel </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A huge variety of <strong>items</strong> to collect and <strong>events</strong> to encounter </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Graphics so good you'll forget <strong>its just a game</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characters with <strong>no</strong> ulterior motives! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And <strong>more</strong>!!  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/726744732bf09fbaa097c97ac8c27f23.poster.avif?t=1739988118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/726744732bf09fbaa097c97ac8c27f23.webm?t=1739988118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/726744732bf09fbaa097c97ac8c27f23.mp4?t=1739988118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/14c22cf84985625154d9a85ed34967fe.avif?t=1739988118\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SPELLHACK!! </strong>is a survival deckbuilder that features fast-paced, arcadey combat and a surreal 1980s setting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the <strong>day</strong>, you have 12 hours to spend improving your Spelldrive and collecting new Technospells. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At <strong>night</strong>, the Summoned Beasts descend upon you. You'll need to think fast to survive  12 hours of nighttime before the next day arrives!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/3a69eb9e9e93b2cc6874d2b6ef8f371a.poster.avif?t=1739988118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/3a69eb9e9e93b2cc6874d2b6ef8f371a.webm?t=1739988118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/3a69eb9e9e93b2cc6874d2b6ef8f371a.mp4?t=1739988118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SPELLHACK!! Floppy Disk Contents:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>Story Mode</strong> to ease into the pace and mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>Challenge Mode with 5 levels</strong>  to really test your skills!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>150+ Technospells</strong> to collect and install </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>50+ Summoned Beasts</strong> to repel </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A huge variety of <strong>items</strong> to collect and <strong>events</strong> to encounter </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Graphics so good you'll forget <strong>its just a game</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characters with <strong>no</strong> ulterior motives! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And <strong>more</strong>!!  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/726744732bf09fbaa097c97ac8c27f23.poster.avif?t=1739988118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/726744732bf09fbaa097c97ac8c27f23.webm?t=1739988118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889780/extras/726744732bf09fbaa097c97ac8c27f23.mp4?t=1739988118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
